name: Happy Diwali
description:
The holiday season has arrived, bringing with it joy, festivities, bright lights, sparkles, snacks, and sweets. Despite the fact that we live in a country where festivals and celebrations take place all year round, Diwali is one of the most eagerly anticipated festivals in the country. Diwali, which will be celebrated on November 4 this year, brings people from all walks of life together to celebrate the triumph of good over evil.

I took this photograph while visiting Varanasi, India.
